com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse
extends SiperianResponse
    Response to GetAssignableUsersForTasksRequest. The response contains a list of user UIDs corresponding to the users who are permitted to have the requested tasks assigned.

    See GetAssignableUsersForTasksRequest for a description of this request.

    Usage Example:

    The following example shows how to print out the response:

    GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse response = (GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse) sipClient.process(request);
    System.out.println("GetAssignableUsersForTasksResponse result: " + response.getUserUids());
    See Also:
    GetAssignableUsersForTasksRequest, Serialized Form

    API Group: Task
